<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5240729>
    dc:description "FIGURE 52. Yunkeracarus muris Fain, 1957, female. A, dorsal view; B, ventral view; C, tarsus I in ventral view; D, same in dorsal view; E, tarsus II in ventral view; F, tarsus III in ventral view; G, tarsus IV in ventral view; H, genu I in lateral view. Scale bars: 100 µm (A, B), 50 µm (C–H)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5240729/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5240731>
    dc:description "FIGURE 53. Yunkeracarus muris Fain, 1957, male. A, gnathosoma in dorsal view; B, same in ventral view; C, chelicera in lateral view; D, fragment of propodonotum; E, opisthosoma in ventral view; F, aedeagus. Scale bars: 100 µm (D, E), 50 µm (A–C, F)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5240731/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

